Update: November 18, 2022
The code has been translated into python3



TOLNET/NDACC Vertical resolution algorithm in python 

The standalone algorithm are in:
ResolutionDF.py
ResolutionIR.py
Running these codes in a standalone mode solves a little example.

The Savitzky-Golay filters are found in:
filtering.py

The comparison of the Python version of the algorithm against Dr. T. Leblanc (JPL) IDL version is found in:
checkresolution.py


